{"type": "article", "id": 19519, "title": "扎哈在曼哈顿设计的住宅，是一幢看起来会流动的建筑", "description": "不得不说，是那种你会盯住看一阵子的房子。", "date": "2015-12-22T15:52:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5164, "name": "曼哈顿"}, {"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}, {"id": 1448, "name": "扎哈·哈迪德"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 353, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162745QjhZqvSzJbpi0AVu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t20 世纪具有革命意义的建筑都在住宅上，但近几年知名的建筑少有住宅作品出现。扎哈·哈迪德在曼哈顿的<a href=\"http://www.520w28.com/architecture\" target=\"_blank\"> 520 west 28th </a>就是她的第一个在城市的住宅项目。尽管整体看过去是个方盒子，波浪纹的表面依然难掩她的个人风格。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这所公寓式的住宅呈现了“L”字形，有 11 层，每一层都覆盖了大面积的整体玻璃，周围用弧形的黑框做结构，有一种收缩的感觉。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>从侧面看，圆弧形的框架也有凹凸起伏，凸出来的地方是住宅的阳台，有非常好的视野。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021627344CuD2hi3dHtkAfrI.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"756\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162735M862PbjaiyKOuQeI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"571\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69804401\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162735wZTiRzkl9UtWO8vj.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162736qoKuLHCOydJc9Qtl.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021627370aygRt7pHrSDPe4W.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162737hrYQo9sc5OVna4Iy.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"756\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\">在直角的转折处做出了“人”字形的结构，有错位的视觉效果，阳光照射在上面，可以看到光影的变化和非常清晰的层次感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021627387gijrUYOVNoDCa4x.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1714\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.58703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t弧形线条和雕塑感延续到了室内，墙面和楼梯都使用了白色，配合着流畅的线条，有音乐感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162739N68w4Vd0cxzFCmRQ.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"665\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021627393USiPF4rTC7tYKWb.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1023\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.25061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这里一共有 39 套独立公寓，最大一套面积可达 500 多平米。</span>房间非常开阔，多使用黑白两色，有现代感。据悉，<span>含有两间卧室的住宅起价 497.5 万美元，4 间卧室的住宅可达 2500 万美元。预计 2016 年建成。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162740DyPOMwv6mqoXxBJk.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162740slPiH2d7tz08Z3jp.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162741nfYU2zGIVCQmT8d7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162741IuGwXj3SQK4pFqAg.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162741Or46ESsFJ8m1KPtz.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"573\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>橱柜来自意大利的顶级橱柜品牌 Boffi</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t此外，整套公寓还包括 IMAX 私人影院、游泳池等公共设施。室内游泳池在顶层，有 75 英尺宽。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162742utgHYiv1jwmWJyx3.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"665\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162743iWdabuQPnxJO8y2g.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"665\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162743ogLhWwkiSI8F1YDs.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"665\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162744V1Fxh8LyEjKNXblP.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"665\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162744D39qaBFAOQ04tYiZ.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"665\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/zaha-hadid-520-west-28th-interiors-chelsea-condos-new-york-high-line-12-19-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}